  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0db4\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb \u0db4\u0dcf\u0da8\u0db8\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc4\u0db3\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Introducing a certificate course in entrepreneurship",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Commercial Bank in association with the Post Graduate Institute of Management (PIM) affiliated to the University of Sri Jayawardenepura has introduced a new certificate course to develop the small and medium entrepreneurship skills of women entrepreneurs.",
        "For this certificate course, 3 rounds of 7-hour lectures will be conducted over a period of three months, and a practical presentation will be held at the end of the course.",
        "Here, lectures will be held on the topics of 'Business Development for Women Entrepreneurs', 'Principles of Negotiating Finance' and 'Innovation and Branding'.",
        "After these lectures, the participants should come up with a practical plan for the introduction of a new product or service, a cost estimate and a marketing plan.",
        "The bank notes that the certificate is awarded to women who complete these presentations and lectures on these three topics.",
        "Topics covered in this course include how to grow a business in tough times. How to find new opportunities? How to develop a business to increase income? How to plan the finances of a business? How to maintain basic accounting records and records of a business? How to budget for a business? How to manage costs? How to reach agreements and build relationships with suppliers? How to plan to introduce a new product and service? How to transition from the role of businesswoman to the role of entrepreneur? How to promote a business through different media? Topics include:"
      ],
